    "We consider several state-of-the-art methods: a) Generalized Cross Entropy (GCE) [12], b) Symmetric Cross Entropy (SCE) [13], c) Partially Huberised Cross Entropy (PHCE) [58], d) Taylor Cross Entropy (TCE) [59], e) Active Passive Loss (APL) [14], specifically NCE+RCE, f) Asymmetric Loss Functions (AFL) [42], specifically NCE+AGCE.",
